"{\"uid\": \"trt.global-afrika-francais-article-18194148\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"L'Alg\\u00e9rienne Imane Khelif a remport\\u00e9 l'or en boxe f\\u00e9minine aux Jeux olympiques de Paris, dans un contexte de controverse sur la parit\\u00e9 hommes-femmes.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13, \"end\": 25, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 63, \"end\": 67, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jeux\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\"}, {\"begin\": 82, \"end\": 87, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.2542969161496376e-43, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 89, \"end\": 93, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"score\": 0.9999999996232418, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"dans\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif, 25 ans, a \\u00e9t\\u00e9 couronn\\u00e9e championne apr\\u00e8s avoir battu la Chinoise Yang Liu 5-0 dans la finale des 66 kg au stade Roland-Garros.\", \"from\": 151, \"to\": 285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"La boxeuse alg\\u00e9rienne avait \\u00e9t\\u00e9 disqualifi\\u00e9e des Championnats du monde 2023 apr\\u00e8s avoir \\u00e9chou\\u00e9 \\u00e0 un test d'\\u00e9ligibilit\\u00e9 de genre.\", \"from\": 287, \"to\": 415, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Il s'agit de la premi\\u00e8re m\\u00e9daille d'or de l'Alg\\u00e9rie en boxe f\\u00e9minine.\", \"from\": 417, \"to\": 486, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00ab Je suis tr\\u00e8s heureuse.\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 512, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Depuis huit ans, c'est mon r\\u00eave et je suis maintenant championne olympique et m\\u00e9daill\\u00e9e d'or \\u00bb, a d\\u00e9clar\\u00e9 Khelif.\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 626, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00ab J'ai travaill\\u00e9 pendant huit ans, je n'ai pas dormi, j'ai travaill\\u00e9 d\\u00fbr pendant huit ans.\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 717, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Maintenant, je suis championne olympique \\u00bb.\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 761, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yang a f\\u00e9licit\\u00e9 Khelif  \\u00ab J'ai fait de mon mieux, mais mon adversaire \\u00e9tait bien meilleure.\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 854, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 818, \"end\": 821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nation_state\", \"score\": 0.9999999991637196, \"rank\": 7.206814819787684e-10, \"text\": \"mon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nation_state\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nation_state\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"C'est une excellente combattante et elle est tr\\u00e8s forte \\u00bb, a d\\u00e9clar\\u00e9 Yang.\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 929, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Le premier match de Khelif aux Jeux de Paris a eu lieu le 1er ao\\u00fbt contre Angela Carini, mais la boxeuse italienne a abandonn\\u00e9 le match apr\\u00e8s 46 secondes.\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 1085, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1005, \"end\": 1018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Apr\\u00e8s avoir re\\u00e7u un coup de poing au visage, Carini s'est retir\\u00e9e dans le coin et a abandonn\\u00e9.\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1181, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1132, \"end\": 1138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9998420679819361, \"rank\": 0.00015795696455871892, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 1153, \"end\": 1157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"score\": 0.9999999996232418, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"dans\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\"}, {\"begin\": 1161, \"end\": 1165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coin\", \"score\": 0.9999997328382407, \"rank\": 2.458847586989018e-07, \"text\": \"coin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00ab Je n'ai pas pu terminer le match.\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1218, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"J'ai ressenti une forte douleur dans le nez \\u00bb, a d\\u00e9clar\\u00e9 Carini.\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1251, \"end\": 1255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"score\": 0.9999999996232418, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"dans\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\"}, {\"begin\": 1276, \"end\": 1282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9998420679819361, \"rank\": 0.00015795696455871892, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Apr\\u00e8s la victoire de la boxeuse alg\\u00e9rienne, Carini s'est excus\\u00e9e de ne pas avoir serr\\u00e9 la main de Khelif.\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1390, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1329, \"end\": 1335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9998420679819361, \"rank\": 0.00015795696455871892, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif a respectivement \\u00e9limin\\u00e9 Carini (pr\\u00e9liminaires), la Hongroise Anna Luca Hamori (quarts de finale) et le Tha\\u00eflandais Janjaem Suwannapheng (demi-finales) avant de battre Yang en finale.\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1582, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1424, \"end\": 1430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9998420679819361, \"rank\": 0.00015795696455871892, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Les Jeux de Paris se termineront dimanche.\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1626, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1588, \"end\": 1592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jeux\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\"}, {\"begin\": 1596, \"end\": 1601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.2542969161496376e-43, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u27a4Suivez-nous sur TRT Afrika Fran\\u00e7ais via notre cha\\u00eene WhatsApp  00:00  00